55:12.720 --> 55:15.180
Hit the track,
hit the... hit the links.

55:15.260 --> 55:18.220
Definitely roll some bocci.

55:18.300 --> 55:20.050
Walk home along
the beach at night.

55:20.130 --> 55:22.180
Kids come down
and visit for the holidays.

55:23.680 --> 55:25.430
BRUNO: Maybe...

55:25.510 --> 55:28.760
meet a nice widow
to share it with.

55:28.840 --> 55:30.930
Uh huh.

55:31.010 --> 55:33.260
That's it.

55:34.800 --> 55:36.970
Go do it.

55:37.050 --> 55:39.590
